`NG1: Object is possibly 'null'. [plugin angular-compiler]`

when we try to access check1 or check2 with this code:

```html
@if (check1 && check2 &&
        {
            allowed: service.BehaviorSubject$ | async
        };
        as viewData ) {
     ...
}

```


if we rewrite the code to this everything works as expected

```html
@if (check1 && check2) {
    @if (
        {
            allowed: service.BehaviorSubject$ | async
        };
        as viewData ) {
     }
    ...
}
